{"tid":1563383,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"強烈要求連仔開個「行動台」","createTime":"2019-09-12T11:24:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-12T18:15:25.000Z","uid":63822,"like":33,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"c5210cc21c5f4f3fd596d5e2a91ec65add65009e","tid":1563383,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:24:54.000Z","msg":"呢位巴打講既野好啱<br />\n<br />\n<blockquote>而家係星期四傍晚，你班撚樣玩夠未？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1563184\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1563184</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不過好多時有新聞、情報出黎，消息太震撼會推走哂行動post<br />\n<br />\n小弟要求連仔開返個行動台，等一眾手足可以隨時知黎緊有乜<br />\n<br />\n出左門口想搵返行動細節，去邊集合/改地點都方便好多<br />\n<br />\n麻煩各位同意既就幫手推比連仔睇"},{"pid":"1894985b5eb2215bfb9011a1115e755760648d84","tid":1563383,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"85fee9e7a35404166c504d5aed8c0505d5443a22","tid":1563383,"uid":237528,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:25:28.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n［重要］外媒讚我地玩人鏈唱國歌式抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kiss.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼￼<br />\n我係香港人呀屌￼￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n香港人繼續自high 啦 又比d 掌聲自己<br />\n屌你地老母 ￼<br />\n出面行動post 又唔見你地推得咁落力<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />￼<br />\n十幾個國歌post ￼Twitter 又全部國歌<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/dead.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n新屋嶺義士呢？￼<br />\nTwitter 我search #sanukling （唔係#sunukling) 得少量post 咩事<br />\n大家可唔可以宣傳下新屋嶺義士被打強姦情況<br />\n引起國際關注￼<br />\n唔好比義士成為condom￼ <br />\n唔好比佢地既血白流<br />\n新屋嶺系核彈 港版集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n全世界今晚集中火力 tag #sanukling # Chinazi #xinjiang #policestate #warcrime￼ <img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n提提大家人權法唔系100%通過￼<br />\n可以加辣亦可以減辣<br />\n之前就受害者模式<br />\n依家就勝利者模式唱國歌<br />\n你估依家美國會唔會幫你加辣￼￼￼<br />\n未通過之前好心大家扮下野啦 ￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n繼續唱美國國歌 揮美國國旗<br />\n同埋做好文宣 咩都好形造到我地有幾慘得幾慘￼<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12bab5b0dc6f5fcdd1a0f16e197519660c6a0010","tid":1563383,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:29:11.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"af0c82d81c80c0378a1bac88fcfd6bd806925786","tid":1563383,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12bab5b0dc6f5fcdd1a0f16e197519660c6a0010","tid":1563383,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:29:11.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"177117d16aa927c79b01bb8da5b9ebaad53fd3c7","tid":1563383,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"af0c82d81c80c0378a1bac88fcfd6bd806925786","tid":1563383,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"12bab5b0dc6f5fcdd1a0f16e197519660c6a0010","tid":1563383,"uid":63822,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:29:11.000Z","msg":"1"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:29:22.000Z","msg":"2"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T11:29:34.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"45dc9ffeaadf496c6591402e0c4efc393aefe93f","tid":1563383,"uid":63822,"like":0,"d